select sql_id,
SQL_fulltext,
USER_IO_WAIT_TIME,
Executions,
elapsed_time,
cpu_time,
disk_reads,
buffer_gets,
PARSING_USER_ID,
parsing_schema_name from 
(select sql_id,
SQL_fulltext,
USER_IO_WAIT_TIME,
Executions,
elapsed_time,
cpu_time,
disk_reads,
buffer_gets,
PARSING_USER_ID,
parsing_schema_name from v$sql
order by last_active_time desc
)
where rownum<11
select name,value from v$sysstat where name='session logical reads'
select name,value from v$sysstat where name='physical read total IO requests'
select size_for_estimate,                      size_factor * 100 f,                    estd_physical_read_time,                estd_physical_reads              from v$db_cache_advice where id = '3'
select java_pool_size_for_estimate s,           java_pool_size_factor * 100 f,           estd_lc_load_time l, 0            from v$java_pool_advice
select TIME_WAITED_MICRO from V$SYSTEM_EVENT  where event = 'Shared IO Pool Memory'
select shared_pool_size_for_estimate s,          shared_pool_size_factor * 100 f,          estd_lc_load_time l, 0             from v$shared_pool_advice
select PGA_TARGET_FOR_ESTIMATE s,          PGA_TARGET_FACTOR * 100 f,           ESTD_TIME t,         BYTES_PROCESSED b   from v$pga_target_advice order by PGA_TARGET_FOR_ESTIMATE
